&lt;/dl></description></item><item><title>细胞死亡</title><link>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8E%E6%8D%9F%E4%BC%A4/%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1/</link><pubDate>Tue, 03 Oct 2023 00:00:28 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://daisilia.com/series/%E7%97%85%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E5%92%8C%E7%BB%84%E7%BB%87%E7%9A%84%E9%80%82%E5%BA%94%E4%B8%8E%E6%8D%9F%E4%BC%A4/%E7%BB%86%E8%83%9E%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1/</guid><description>&lt;p>当细胞发生致死性代谢、结构和功能障碍，便可引起&lt;strong>细胞不可逆性损伤&lt;/strong>，即&lt;strong>细胞死亡&lt;/strong>。&lt;/p>
